# Mythos — withmythos.com

## What This Is
Coming-soon landing page for Mythos, a creative studio at the intersection of ancient storytelling and modern systems. "Myth + OS." The name is shared with Anthropic's leaked "Claude Mythos" model, which drives organic search traffic. Josh Walker owns the domain and @WithMythos on X.

## Architecture
Single self-contained HTML file. No framework, no build tools.
- `index.html` — the entire site
- `../assets/mythos-logo.svg` — logo wordmark (Illustrator export, inlined in HTML)

## Stack
- Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS
- Tailwind-free (pure CSS custom properties)
- Google Fonts CDN: Cormorant Garamond (serif) + Inter (sans)
- Intersection Observer for scroll-driven reveal animations

## Design System
See `STYLE-GUIDE.md` for full reference. Key points:
- Warm cream background (#F2EFE8), ink-dark text (#2C2A28)
- Cormorant Garamond 300 weight for all headings
- Alternating pattern: normal weight declarations + italic lighter-ink sub-lines
- Left/right/center alignment alternates section to section
- Blur-to-sharp reveal animations on scroll (1.6s cubic-bezier)
- Noise texture overlay + subtle vignette

## Copy Voice
Jack Butcher style. Short declarative lines. Line breaks do the structural work. No hedging, no softeners, no transitional phrases. Every word earns its place.

## Deployment
Target: Cloudflare Pages connected to this repo. Domain: withmythos.com

## What's Not Built Yet
- Email capture backend (form exists, no submission handler)
- OG image for social sharing
- Favicon
- Analytics (GA4 or Plausible)
